729378f-b.title: Richmond: Richmond Road - Altamount Street
729378f-b.text:
Richmond Road, north side, west of Altamount Street.
Shown is the Boy Scout Cabin and ruins, situated, according
to P. L. perr, southwest of the Moravian -emetery. The
Richmond Road desipnation is an approximate location,
the writer of these lines being unable to determine,
with uncuestionable accuracy, the exact site of the cabin.
View 1: January 10, 1924
View 2: March 27, 1924
By Wm. T. Davis through P. L. Sperr
NO REPRCDTTTIONS
